---
title: Cozy Tofu and Pesto Orzo with Spinach and Peas
description: This drool-worthy orzo dish is creamy and luscious without being too heavy! It's made even more enticing with a hit of fragrant basil pesto bringing herbaceous goodness and green veggies adding some balance. A zesty-garlic seasoned tofu steak is perfect to top it all off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/orzo-au-tofu-et-au-pesto-e000e98d.jpg
